Name: uDom-Admins-AD-ENG
Description: uDom admins who are domain local admins.

Name: uDom-Admins-AD-OPS
Description: uDom admins who administrate AD, but are NOT domain admins.

Name: uDom-Admins-PKI
Description: uDom members granted local administrator rights on PKI servers.

Name: uDom-SVR-Auditors
Description: uDom members granted rights to read security logs on member servers.

Name: uDom-SVR-Auditors-DCs
Description: uDom members granted rights to read security logs on domain controllers.

Name: uDom-SVR-Local-Admins
Description: uDom members granted local administrator rights on member servers.

Name: uDom-SVR-Local-Admins-DCs
Description: uDom members granted local administrator rights on domain controllers.

Name: uDom-SVR-RSA-NoChallenge
Description: uDom members are not required to use RSA to logon. Member of SVR-RSA-NoChallenge.

Name: uDom-WKS-Local-Admins
Description: uDom members granted local administrator rights on workstations.

Name: uDom-WKS-RSA-NoChallenge
Description: uDom members are not required to use RSA to logon. Member of WKS-RSA-NoChallenge.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageAD
Description: uDom members that have full control of \nbN\* OUs.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageAD-ENG
Description: uDom members that are delegated most rights granted to Domain Admins.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageGroups
Description: uDom members that can manage AD groups under \nbN OU.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManagePKI
Description: uDom members that can publish and manage PKI in AD.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageSVRCompObjs
Description: uDom members that can join servers to the domain.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageUsers
Description: uDom members that can manage AD users under \nbN OU.

Name: uDom-DelegatedRight-ManageWKSCompObjs
Description: uDom members that can join workstations to the domain.
